duties_responsibilities.duty: Perform material handling duties such as operating equipment for product receiving, disbursement, and inventory checks.
Input daily item orders, perform daily stock checks, and ensure inventory items are counted, rotated, and replenished daily.
Receive inbound materials, mark materials with identifying information, and record the amount of material received.
Arrange materials for order assembly, perform quality control, and move carts to and from loading docks.
Assist with customer requests while maintaining a high level of customer service and perform housekeeping duties including onsite cleanup.
